CmvHBE7R8uHA">Tặng nội (I) - 贈內（I）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Tu%C3%A2n-H%E1%BA%A1c/Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Gi%C3%A1p-Th%E1%BA%A1ch-huy%E1%BB%87n-b%E1%BB%87nh-t%E1%BA%A9u/poem-tzYn8zmk-NB-ezMvm6LM8A">Thương Giáp Thạch huyện bệnh tẩu - 傷硤石縣病叟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Tu%C3%A2n-H%E1%BA%A1c/author-qyiAcaE2MOeOx-crtOo0SA">Đỗ Tuân Hạc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-M%E1%BA%ADt/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-t%C3%ACnh-bi%E1%BB%83u/poem-AGKUOTf4MNBoRtTrY2zw2A">Trần tình biểu - 陳情表</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-M%E1%BA%ADt/author-2WZpsdSFEWvTQerf8uTifQ">Lý Mật</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A2n-Kh%C3%AD-T%E1%BA%ADt/V%C4%A9nh-ng%E1%BB%99-l%E1%BA%A1c-Kinh-kh%E1%BA%A9u-B%E1%BA%AFc-C%E1%BB%91-%C4%91%C3%ACnh-ho%C3%A0i-c%E1%BB%95/poem-BvX7SZcYDh6BIaZimIwj-Q">Vĩnh ngộ lạc - Kinh khẩu Bắc Cố đình hoài cổ - 永遇樂－京口北顧亭懷古</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A2n-Kh%C3%AD-T%E1%BA%ADt/author-cR0yq4BrF6xGIKZCvJGLSA">Tân Khí Tật</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
